# Core Data Types

## Hierarchy
`WorkspaceDoc` → `FactoryRecord[]` → `tree: TreeNode` → `children: TreeNode[]`

## `FlowNode` — `src/lib/flowChartModel.ts`
The machine data at a node. Key fields:
- `outputItemKey`, `outputItemName`, `buildingKey`, `buildingName`
- `recipeKey`, `recipeName` (optional — absent on extractors)
- `outputPerMachine`, `inputPerMachine` (0 on extractors → `isRaw = true`)
- `count`, `clockPercent`, `machineClockPercents?`, `totalOutput`
- `isRaw: boolean`, `nodePurity?`

## `TreeNode` — `src/lib/flowChartModel.ts`
Wraps a FlowNode in a tree. Key fields:
- `id` (mirrors `node.id`), `node: FlowNode`, `children: TreeNode[]`, `parentId`
- `incomingBeltKey?`, `inputEdges?: InputEdge[]`
- `displaySliceIndex?` — which visual column the node appears in (horizontal layout)
- `displayColumnPosition?` — sort order within a column

## `InputEdge` — `src/lib/flowChartModel.ts`
Links a node to a non-parent supplier: `{ itemKey, producerId, beltKey }`.

## `WorkspaceDoc` / `FactoryRecord` — `src/lib/chartStorage.ts`
- `WorkspaceDoc`: `id`, `name`, `factories: FactoryRecord[]`, `updatedAt`
- `FactoryRecord`: `id`, `name`, `tree`, `exports`, `imports`, `storageReserves?`, `autoBalanceEnabled?`, `preferredBeltKey?`
- `FactoryExport` / `FactoryImport`: shared `id`, `itemKey`, `ratePerMin`; cross-link by factory id

## `MachineOption` — `src/components/flow-chart/flowChartTypes.ts`
Recipe-derived tuple for the Add Machine modal:
`{ recipeKey, recipeName, buildingKey, buildingName, outputItemKey, outputPerMachine, inputPerMachine }`

## Key Constants
| Symbol | File | Value |
|--------|------|-------|
| `EMPTY_TREE` | `FlowChart.tsx` | `createTreeNode(createNode("",…), null)` — placeholder root |
| `FLOW_CHART_BELTS` | `flowChartConstants.ts` | All belts sorted by rate |
| `DEFAULT_PREFERRED_BELT` | `chartStorage.ts` | `"belt4"` (Mk.4) |

## Power Generator Extension Types
- `PowerGeneratorOption` — `src/lib/powerGenerators.ts`  
  Pseudo machine-option shape for generator support without replacing base dataset:
  `{ recipeKey, recipeName, buildingKey, buildingName, outputItemKey: "power", outputPerMachine, inputPerMachine, inputsPerMinute[] }`

- `NodePowerDisplay` — `src/lib/flowChartPower.ts`  
  Derived UI power metric per node: `{ isGenerating: boolean, mw: number }`

## Build Inventory Types
- `BuildInventoryResult` — `src/lib/flowChartBuildInventory.ts`  
  Build-sheet rows keyed by machine + produced item for both factory and workspace scopes:
  `{ rows: { buildingKey, buildingName, itemKey, itemName, count, shardsPerMachine, buildIngredients? }[], powerShards }`
